This work was packaged for Debian by:

    OTB Team <contact@orfeo-toolbox.org> on Tue, 29 Nov 2012 11:40:02 +0100

It was downloaded from <http://hg.orfeo-toolbox.org/>, using command:

    hg clone -r <version> http://hg.orfeo-toolbox.org/OTB-Wrapping

The source tarball is an aggregate of several different works in which the
main one, developed by the CNES (Centre National d'Etudes Spatiales), is
Orfeo-Toolbox (OTB) wrappings. Other works include PyGCCXML.

* PyGCCXML (http://www.language-binding.net/pygccxml/pygccxml.html),
  distributed under the Boost Software License 1.0
  (revised BSD-like, see Copyright/PyGCCXMLCopyright.txt)


